author: @batotit
text:
Things I noticed:
1. After watching lots of twice, Itzy, NMIXX, and even JYP dance practices, this room is very familiar to me now :D It is nice to see the edges. 

2. Dahyun is really the introvert of the group. It is not that she is aloof, but she prefers to be on her own most of the time. It is kinda surprising since she is always the one who is presented to be the eccentric weirdo in the group when they are being interviewed or in a reality game.

3. 9:46 Jungyoung is really closed to the trainer, and she is always the one talking to her, maybe even on behalf of the group.

4. I've always been a fan of nayeon and through her, I started following twice. All of them are really pretty. But Sana's beauty somehow is really blooming ever since "I can't stop me." I cant stop crushing on her. She is so handsome!

5. I'm a very cynical person, and I normally roll my eyes when artists give platitudes to other artists. It always feels so fake. But I'm really surprised that the members actually like each other and are real friends.
